---
layout: base.njk
metaTitle: "Contact & Grievances — RURR Advisors"
description: "Contact RURR Advisors, a SEBI Registered Investment Adviser, for a no-obligation consultation — or raise, track and escalate an investor grievance. Compliance officer, SCORES and ODR escalation, and monthly complaints data."
---
<section class="page active" id="page-contact">
  <div class="page-head">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="crumb reveal">Contact &amp; grievances</p>
      <h1 class="reveal">Talk to us, or raise a concern.</h1>
      <p class="reveal">Start a no-obligation conversation about your goals, or formally raise and track an investor grievance. Both reach us directly.</p>
      <div class="head-jump reveal" role="navigation" aria-label="Jump to section">
        <a href="#enquiry">General enquiry</a>
        <a href="#grievances">Raise a grievance</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ A · GENERAL ENQUIRY ============ -->
  <div class="section wrap" id="enquiry">
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Enquiry form</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3.4vw,2.2rem);margin-bottom:24px;">How can we help?</h2>
        <form id="contactForm" novalidate>
          <div class="field"><label for="cName">Full name</label><input id="cName" name="name" type="text" placeholder="Your name" autocomplete="name" required /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="cEmail">Email</label><input id="cEmail" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" autocomplete="email" required /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="cPhone">Phone</label><input id="cPhone" name="phone" type="tel" inputmode="tel" placeholder="+919876543210" autocomplete="tel" required /></div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="cInterest">I'm interested in</label>
            <select id="cInterest" name="interest">
              <option>Financial Planning</option>
              <option>Investment Advisory</option>
              <option>Portfolio Review</option>
              <option>Goal-Based Planning</option>
              <option>Something else</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="field"><label for="cMsg">Message</label><textarea id="cMsg" name="message" placeholder="A few lines about what you're looking for"></textarea></div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" id="cSubmit" type="submit">Send enquiry <span class="arr">→</span></button>
          <p class="form-note">Your details are sent securely to our advisory team. We will never ask for passwords, OTPs, or trading credentials.</p>
          <div class="form-success" id="cSuccess">Thanks — your enquiry has been received. We'll be in touch shortly.</div>
          <div class="form-error" id="cError">Sorry, we couldn't send your enquiry just now. Please try again, or email us at {{ site.email | mailto | safe }}.</div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <aside>
        <div class="contact-info reveal">
          <h3>Reach us</h3>
          <p style="color:#b7c2dd;font-size:.92rem;">SEBI Registered Investment Adviser · Reg. No. {{ site.regNo }}</p>
          <div class="info-row"><div class="l">Office address</div><div class="d">{{ site.address.line1 }},<br>{{ site.address.line2 }}</div></div>
          <div class="info-row"><div class="l">Phone</div><div class="d" style="font-family:var(--mono);">{{ site.phone | whatsapp | safe }}</div></div>
          <div class="info-row"><div class="l">Email</div><div class="d" style="font-family:var(--mono);">{{ site.email | mailto | safe }}</div></div>
          <div class="info-row"><div class="l">Hours</div><div class="d">{{ site.hours }}</div></div>
          <p style="color:#b7c2dd;font-size:.9rem;margin:22px 0 0;">Filing a complaint instead? Head to <a href="#grievances" style="color:var(--brass-soft);text-decoration:underline;">investor grievances</a> below — it has a dedicated complaint desk and escalation matrix.</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ B · INVESTOR GRIEVANCES ============ -->
  <div class="section section--wash-navy section--seam" id="grievances">
   <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Investor grievances</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.9rem,3.8vw,2.6rem)">Raise, track and resolve complaints.</h2>
      <p class="lead" style="font-size:1.05rem;margin-top:1rem;">We take every complaint seriously and aim to redress it promptly — and in any case no later than <strong>21 days</strong> of receipt, as prescribed by SEBI.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Redressal process -->
    <div class="cards" style="margin-bottom:54px;">
      <article class="card reveal">
        <p class="num">Step 01</p>
        <h3>Raise with us</h3>
        <p>Submit your complaint using the desk below, or email our Compliance Officer at {{ site.grievanceEmail | mailto("grievance") | safe }}. You'll receive a ticket number on acknowledgement.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card reveal">
        <p class="num">Step 02</p>
        <h3>We investigate</h3>
        <p>We acknowledge promptly and work to resolve your complaint fairly, within the timelines prescribed by SEBI. Track progress any time with your ticket number.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card reveal">
        <p class="num">Step 03</p>
        <h3>Escalate to SEBI</h3>
        <p>If it remains unresolved or you're not satisfied, escalate via the SEBI SCORES portal ({{ site.scores | weblink | safe }}) or the Online Dispute Resolution portal ({{ site.odr | weblink | safe }}).</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <!-- Complaint desk: raise + track -->
    <div class="grv-tools">
      <!-- RAISE -->
      <div class="tool-card reveal">
        <h3>Raise a new complaint</h3>
        <p class="tc-sub">Fill in your details and we'll generate a ticket number. A confirmation is emailed to you.</p>
        <form id="grvForm" novalidate>
          <div class="field"><label for="gName">Full name</label><input id="gName" name="name" type="text" placeholder="Your name" autocomplete="name" required /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="gEmail">Email</label><input id="gEmail" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" autocomplete="email" required /></div>
          <div class="field"><label for="gPhone">Phone</label><input id="gPhone" name="phone" type="tel" inputmode="tel" placeholder="+919876543210" autocomplete="tel" required /></div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="gCat">Nature of complaint</label>
            <select id="gCat" name="category">
              <option>Advisory service</option>
              <option>Fees / billing</option>
              <option>Communication / response time</option>
              <option>Data / privacy</option>
              <option>Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="field"><label for="gMsg">Describe your complaint</label><textarea id="gMsg" name="details" placeholder="Tell us what happened" required></textarea></div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" id="gSubmit" type="submit">Submit complaint <span class="arr">→</span></button>
          <p class="form-note">We never ask for passwords, OTPs, or trading credentials.</p>
          <div class="result" id="gResult">
            <p style="margin:0 0 .4rem;color:var(--ink);font-weight:600;">Complaint registered</p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 .9rem;color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem;">Save your ticket number — a confirmation has been sent to <span id="gEmailEcho" style="font-family:var(--mono)"></span>.</p>
            <span class="ticket-badge" id="gTicket">RA-0000-00000</span>
            <p class="form-note" style="margin-top:12px;">Use this number under “Track a complaint” to see updates.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="form-error" id="gError">Sorry, we couldn't register your complaint just now. Please try again, or email {{ site.grievanceEmail | mailto("grievance") | safe }}.</div>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- TRACK -->
      <div class="tool-card reveal">
        <h3>Track a complaint</h3>
        <p class="tc-sub">Enter the ticket number you received to view the latest status.</p>
        <form id="trackForm" novalidate>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="tNum">Ticket number</label>
            <input id="tNum" name="ticket" type="text" placeholder="RA-2026-XXXXX" style="font-family:var(--mono);text-transform:uppercase;" />
          </div>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" id="tSubmit" type="submit">Check status <span class="arr">→</span></button>
        </form>

        <div class="result" id="tResult">
          <div class="stepper" id="tStepper" role="list" aria-label="Complaint status">
            <div class="stp" data-stage="1" role="listitem"><span class="dot"></span>Received</div>
            <div class="stp" data-stage="2" role="listitem"><span class="dot"></span>Under review</div>
            <div class="stp" data-stage="3" role="listitem"><span class="dot"></span>Resolved</div>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top:16px;">
            <div class="meta-row"><span class="l">Ticket</span><span class="v" id="tOutNum"></span></div>
            <div class="meta-row"><span class="l">Status</span><span class="v" id="tOutStatus"></span></div>
            <div class="meta-row"><span class="l">Raised on</span><span class="v" id="tOutOpened"></span></div>
            <div class="meta-row"><span class="l">Last update</span><span class="v" id="tOutUpdated"></span></div>
            <div class="meta-row"><span class="l">Expected resolution</span><span class="v" id="tOutEta"></span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="result notfound" id="tNotFound">
          <p style="margin:0;">We couldn't find a complaint with that ticket number. Check the number, or raise a new complaint on the left.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="form-error" id="tError">Sorry, we couldn't look up that ticket just now. Please try again in a moment.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Compliance officer + escalation matrix -->
    <div class="officer-grid" style="margin-top:40px;">
      <div class="contact-info reveal">
        <h3>Compliance Officer</h3>
        <p style="color:#b7c2dd;font-size:.92rem;">Your first point of contact for any grievance.</p>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="l">Name</div><div class="d">{{ site.complianceOfficer.name }}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="l">Email</div><div class="d" style="font-family:var(--mono);">{{ site.complianceOfficer.email | mailto("grievance") | safe }}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="l">Phone</div><div class="d" style="font-family:var(--mono);">{{ site.complianceOfficer.phone | whatsapp("grievance") | safe }}</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-info reveal" style="background:var(--pine);">
        <h3>Escalation matrix</h3>
        <p style="color:#b7c2dd;font-size:.92rem;">If your complaint isn't resolved at one level, escalate to the next.</p>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="l">Level 1 · within 2 working days</div><div class="d">Compliance Officer — {{ site.complianceOfficer.name }}<br><span style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.85rem;color:#c4cee3;">{{ site.complianceOfficer.email | mailto("grievance") | safe }}</span></div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="l">Level 2 · if unresolved in 21 days</div><div class="d">SEBI SCORES portal<br><span style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.85rem;color:#c4cee3;">{{ site.scores | weblink | safe }}</span></div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="l">Level 3 · post-SCORES</div><div class="d">Online Dispute Resolution<br><span style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:.85rem;color:#c4cee3;">{{ site.odr | weblink | safe }}</span></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ C · COMPLAINTS DATA ============ -->
  <div class="section section--wash-green" id="complaints-data">
   <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Transparency</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3.4vw,2.3rem)">Investor complaints data</h2>
      <p class="lead" style="font-size:1.02rem;margin-top:1rem;">Compiled automatically from our complaints register, in the format prescribed by SEBI. <span id="cdAsOf"></span></p>
    </div>

    <p class="form-note" id="cdLoading">Loading the latest complaints data…</p>
    <div class="form-error" id="cdError">Live complaints data is temporarily unavailable. Please try again shortly.</div>
    <noscript><p class="form-note">Please enable JavaScript to view the latest complaints data, or contact us for the current figures.</p></noscript>

    <div id="cdTables" hidden>
      <!-- Table 1: complaints by source for the month -->
      <div style="overflow-x:auto;">
        <table class="data-table">
          <caption id="cdT1Caption">Table 1 — Data for the month</caption>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Sr. No.</th>
              <th>Received from</th>
              <th>Pending end of last month</th>
              <th>Received</th>
              <th>Resolved</th>
              <th>Total pending*</th>
              <th>Pending &gt; 3 months</th>
              <th>Avg. resolution time^ (days)</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="cdT1Body"></tbody>
        </table>
        <p class="form-note" style="margin-top:10px;">* Inclusive of complaints pending as on the last day of the month. ^ Average resolution time is the total time taken to resolve complaints in the month, divided by the number resolved.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Table 2: monthly trend -->
      <div style="overflow-x:auto;margin-top:26px;">
        <table class="data-table">
          <caption>Table 2 — Trend of monthly disposal of complaints</caption>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Sr. No.</th>
              <th>Month</th>
              <th>Carried forward from previous month</th>
              <th>Received</th>
              <th>Resolved</th>
              <th>Pending*</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="cdT2Body"></tbody>
        </table>
        <p class="form-note" style="margin-top:10px;">* Inclusive of complaints pending as on the last day of the month.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Table 3: annual trend -->
      <div style="overflow-x:auto;margin-top:26px;">
        <table class="data-table">
          <caption>Table 3 — Trend of annual disposal of complaints</caption>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Sr. No.</th>
              <th>Year</th>
              <th>Carried forward from previous year</th>
              <th>Received</th>
              <th>Resolved</th>
              <th>Pending</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="cdT3Body"></tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
</section>
